name: The Boys
detail: The Boys is a dark and irreverent superhero TV series that explores the gritty and corrupt side of celebrity superheroes, depicting a group of vigilantes who take on superpowered individuals gone rogue while exposing the dark secrets of the powerful corporation that manages them.

name: Money Heist
detail: To carry out the biggest heist in history, a mysterious man called The Professor recruits a band of eight robbers who have a single characteristic: none of them has anything to lose

name: John Wick
detail: John Wick is a relentless and stylish action film series that follows the titular retired hitman, played by Keanu Reeves, as he seeks vengeance for the death of his beloved dog, unleashing a wave of meticulously choreographed and brutal retribution against the criminal underworld.

name: Ant Man
detail: Ant-Man is a Marvel superhero film centered around Scott Lang, a skilled thief turned miniature-sized hero, armed with a suit that grants him the ability to shrink in size while increasing in strength.

name: Avengers
detail: The Avengers is a blockbuster Marvel film that unites iconic superheroes like Iron Man, Captain America, Thor, and the Hulk, as they form an extraordinary team to save the world from imminent threats, showcasing epic battles and camaraderie on a global scale.

name: Moon Knight
detail: Moon Knight is a Marvel superhero series that follows the complex and mysterious character Marc Spector, a former Marine and mercenary with dissociative identity disorder, as he becomes the conduit for the Egyptian moon god Khonshu, leading to a gripping exploration of heroism and mental health.

name: Kota Factory
detail: Kota Factory is a critically acclaimed Indian web series that chronicles the trials and tribulations of students preparing for competitive exams in the educational hub of Kota, blending humor and realism to portray the intense academic pressure and camaraderie among peers.

name: Collage Romance
detail: College Romance is a popular Indian web series that navigates the amusing and relatable adventures of three college friends as they navigate love, friendships, and the challenges of university life, capturing the essence of youthful exuberance.

name: Thor Love Of Thunder
detail: Thor: Love and Thunder is an upcoming Marvel film that promises a cosmic spectacle, combining the godly might of Thor, played by Chris Hemsworth, with the enchanting chaos of Natalie Portman's Jane Foster as the mighty Thor, exploring love, thunderous battles, and the multiverse.

name: Uncharted
detail: Uncharted is a film adaptation of the popular video game series, featuring Tom Holland as a young Nathan Drake embarking on a globe-trotting adventure, combining action, treasure hunting, and a charismatic lead.

name: Eesho
detail: Eesho is an Indian Malayalam-language drama thriller film film directed by Nadirshah featuring Jayasurya and Namitha Pramod in the lead roles

name: Top Gun
detail: Top Gun is a classic action film that follows Maverick, a talented fighter pilot played by Tom Cruise, as he undergoes intense training at the Top Gun Naval Fighter Weapons School, blending aerial dogfights, camaraderie, and romance.

name: Jurassic World
detail: Jurassic World is a thrilling science fiction franchise that resurrects the concept of dinosaur amusement parks with cutting-edge genetic engineering, unleashing chaos as prehistoric creatures wreak havoc on unsuspecting visitors.

name: Eternals
detail: Eternals is a Marvel film that introduces a powerful immortal alien race, the Eternals, as they reunite to protect Earth from ancient adversaries, exploring cosmic mythology and the consequences of their millennia-long presence on the planet.

name: Spider Man
detail: Spider-Man is a beloved superhero franchise that follows the adventures of Peter Parker, a high school student with arachnid abilities, as he swings between balancing his dual life, facing iconic villains, and embodying the friendly neighborhood hero in the Marvel Universe.
